  m_text: "LHAnimationClipPlayer is a function for playing AnimationClips.\nIts key
    feature is the ability to seek to the initial and final values \u200B\u200Bin
    units of the smallest AnimationClip.\nBecause it can be executed before Awake
    (before the screen is displayed), it is ideal for UI In/Out animations."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 47d19175fae931641a776c994c1e67dd, type: 2}
